\begin_layout Subsection
UX diagrams
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The UX diagram (
\emph on
UsereXperience diagram
\emph default
) shows the organization of the screens and the user can navigate among
 them.
 In this section we will provide the diagrams for the unregistered passenger,
 the registered passenger and the taxi driver
\end_layout

